{"tid":1787060,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"最新和理非職業—人像攝影師","createTime":"2019-12-17T15:22:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T19:56:00.000Z","uid":175453,"like":24,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9973673515365936ed530c796a86fd66ba2caeea","tid":1787060,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:22:50.000Z","msg":"大家有冇試過，係出面食野戈陣 <br />\n間舖頭外面有d仆街眼金金咁望住你<br />\n戈種感覺真係極度難頂。<br />\n<br />\n依家，我地要活學活用。<br />\n每日7-8點或者lunchtime ，你行過每一間藍店，你唔洗裝修佢。<br />\n你淨係需要<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">zoom大班死港豬塊面影</span></span><br />\n最好就等成班豬排緊隊戈陣影。間舖有玻璃就影埋入面。記得唔好陰d陰d影，而係要大大力影，最好話埋比佢知我地影緊你就得。<br />\n等你班仆街仲咁開心日日係到食元氣，美心。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">日影夜影，班仆街自然會避免選擇呢類垃圾舖頭！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">唔係大範圍影舖頭，而係集中近距離影d仆街</span></span><br />\n<br />\n優點：<br />\n1:入藍店好似入左動物園，比人影比人觀賞<br />\n2:用行動話人知邊d係藍店<br />\n3.容易執行不犯法，街坊裝就得<br />\n4.比遠處藍絲見到，以為人多而唔行去食<br />\n5.到到都有手足，你一個人做慢慢就愈黎愈多人跟機。<br />\n<br />\n1個人做緊係冇效，你試下排排下隊突然有成十幾條友係到影你同啤你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比我都走啦。亦都唔洗叫口號！唔洗同人爭執，一嘈就轉個圈再番黎搞尻佢，主要係令班藍絲同偽黃生理上接受唔到間舖頭！<br />\n<br />\n缺點：<br />\n1:浪費電話memory <br />\n2:污染部電話<br />\n<br />\n有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31699b006ec044781dd87f8e369732b1b1fb1700","tid":1787060,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:24:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">12.22  愛丁堡<br />\n12.21  721五個月 <br />\n12.24 和你shop<br />\n12.24  夜晚尖咀見<br />\n12.31  和你拖<br />\n2020.1.1元旦大遊行</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H5GFOEY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH5GFOEY.jpg&h=f6d37c78&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VBcxEME.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVBcxEME.jpg&h=7ab8f960&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NKLvrrF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNKLvrrF.jpg&h=653d2ffc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mY6iAj1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmY6iAj1.jpg&h=c159792d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5tVOXym.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5tVOXym.jpg&h=2b5d9c8e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mwHNtE2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmwHNtE2.jpg&h=b700f53b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06d69dd2d70fea318f32efa958d4d5c319648d10","tid":1787060,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:24:29.000Z","msg":"影到日日都去動物園<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b176ff541572045b1863908ff15820e124a1e0ed","tid":1787060,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:26:45.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"615958a53b68d8daffa58776ca5a4513296edbde","tid":1787060,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:28:22.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"5d6a93a29a029e6f960dac419c88338611c555c7","tid":1787060,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:29:24.000Z","msg":"裝修係物理層面<br />\n和理非都要係精神層面幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52860df83b48434464f0100544b368645ef29841","tid":1787060,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:33: